A small update to all Steam games has been released tonight. Changes included are:<br/><br/><ul style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><li>Allow Counter-Strike: Condition Zero to run as a dedicated server under Windows</li><br/><li>Prevent the "connection to server lost due to level change" error</li><br/></ul><br/>Only Condition Zero dedicated servers need to update. Admins of other dedicated servers don't need to update.<br/></p>
